        "description": "An event attributed to an unknown person. If you provide an `anonymous_id` with the event, you can associate the event with a person later (using the anonymous ID).",
        "oneOf": [
          {
            "title": "Standard anonymous event",
            "type": "object",
            "required": [
              "name"
